Uropodella
is considered basal to all other taxa of the Sejina sensu stricto (
). The Sejina sensu stricto consists of one superfamily, Sejoidea , with four families, Sejidae , Uropodellidae , Ichthyostomatogasteridae , and Reginacharlottiidae (
;
). In turn, the Uropodellidae contains only a single genus,
